BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td ('I can't,' Cumulus said. 'If I rain, I'll get all dark and small and everyone will see my) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (feelings.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td ('What's wrong with that?' Drizzle asked gently. 'I rain every other day. It feels) Tj ET
