BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Cumulus floated beside him gently. 'I used to think that too. Want to know what happened) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (to me?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (He told his whole story   the holding, the heaviness, the girl on the hill, and finally) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (letting go.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td ('After I rained,' Cumulus said, 'I felt the best I'd ever felt. Lighter than air. Try it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (I'll rain with you.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: Cumulus floating beside another small puffy cloud who looks heavy and gray,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (talking gently to him, offering to rain together, a supportive friend helping another open) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (up]) Tj ET
endstream
