BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Together, the two clouds rained side by side. The little cloud's first rain was small and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (timid.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (But Cumulus cheered him on: 'That's it! Let it go! You're doing great!') Tj ET
