BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (from both of them.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (Afterward, the little cloud was light and floating high. 'That felt INCREDIBLE! Why did I) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (wait so long?') Tj ET
