BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 20) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (The little girl on the hill? Her dog got better. And she still visited Cumulus whenever he) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (floated low.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td ('Thank you,' she told him once. 'Watching you rain taught me something too.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td ('What's that?' Cumulus asked.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td ('That everyone needs to let their feelings out   even big, strong clouds. It doesn't make) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (us weak. It makes us real.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (They sat together in comfortable silence, the girl and the cloud, two beings who) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (understood that feelings are meant to flow, not to be dammed up inside.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: The girl sitting on her hill, healthy dog beside her, waving up at Cumulus) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (who floats happily above, both peaceful and emotionally healthy, a warm friendship scene]) Tj ET
endstream
