BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Cumulus also learned when to ask for help. Sometimes his feelings were too big for just) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (rain.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (On those days, he'd float to his mother Nimbus, or find Drizzle, or seek out the girl on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (the hill.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td ('I'm having a really hard day,' he'd say. And they would simply be there with him.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (He learned that you don't always have to weather the storm alone. Sometimes the bravest) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (thing is saying: I need help. I need someone to be with me.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (And there was always someone willing to be there.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: Cumulus with friends around him on a hard day   Nimbus nearby, Drizzle, the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (girl below   supported and not alone, showing that asking for help is also okay]) Tj ET
