BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (human.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.4 Td ([Illustration: A permission slip drawn beautifully with cloud borders, giving children) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td (permission to feel all their feelings, signed with a cloud stamp, warm and validating and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (empowering]) Tj ET
