BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And after the rain comes the rainbow. After the tears comes the lightness. After the storm) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (comes the clearest sky you have ever seen.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (So let it rain when it needs to. Let the feelings flow.) Tj ET
