stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (It's Okay to Cry - Emotions Are Natural and Helpful) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (Cumulus learned that holding in your feelings doesn't make you strong   it makes you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (heavy. Tears, like rain, are natural and necessary. They help you process hard feelings,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (release tension, and make room for happiness again. Everyone cries sometimes   even) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (grown-ups, even tough people, even clouds! After you let your feelings out, you always) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (feel lighter. So never be ashamed of your tears. They are proof that you feel deeply, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.4 Td (that is a beautiful thing.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
