BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.8 Td (etc.\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 557.0 Td (4. How did Cumulus's rain help the valley below? How might your feelings help people) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 543.0 Td (around you?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 519.2 Td (5. What would you say to a friend who was embarrassed about crying?) Tj ET
